define the path accurately


Step 1: 
       npm init -y


Step 2:
       npm install -D tailwindcss


Step 3:
       npm i tailwindcss@3 postcss autoprefixer   -  to use older version


Step 4:
       npx tailwindcss init



Step 5: 
       create src folder and create input.css file and src folder


Step 6:
       in tailwind.config.js file, contentshould be: ["*.html"]


Step 7:
       npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./src/output.css --watch

Step 8:
      link output.css file to html which is created:
       "link rel="stylesheet" href="./src/input.css">















Additional :


